    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a mathematically preserved A80 Supra Turbo, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six power plant in its original sequential twin-turbocharged configuration. This specimen retains its factory-spec longitudinal layout with zero modifications to the forced induction system or ECU mapping. The drivetrain is anchored by the coveted Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission, feeding power through a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless: compression tests show nominal, consistent PSI across all six cylinders, and the cooling system remains pressurized with no thermal fatigue evident on the radiator end tanks or hoses. The chassis integrity is superlative, with all factory spot welds intact and a double-wishbone suspension geometry that remains as tight as the day it left the line. All bushings are supple, and the undercarriage is devoid of oxidation or fluid weeping, confirming its climate-controlled history. This is a purist\u2019s investment, free of the typical aftermarket interference or structural wear found in this segment.",
